erture\"\n* \"Natsu no Namae\"\n* \"Subarashiki Sekai\"\n* \"Yes? No?\"}}\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Arashic]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Runaway Train\"\n* \"Raise Your Hands\"\n* \"Cool & Soul\"\n* \"Secret Eyes\"}}\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Time (Arashi album)|Time]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Wave\"\n* \"Firefly\"\n* \"Taiy\u014d no Sekai\"\n* \"Rock You\"\n* \"Cry For You\"\n* \"Kaze\"\n* \"Life\"\n* \"Can't Let You Go\"}}\n|-\n| 2008 \n| ''[[Dream \"A\" Live]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Move You Body\"\n* \"Niji no Kanata e\"\n* \"Flashback\"\n* \"My Answer\"\n* \"Once Again\"\n* \"Hip Hop Boogie\"}}\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[All the Best! 1999\u20132009]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Re(mark)able\"\n* \"5x10\"}}\n|-\n| 2010 \n| ''[[Boku no Miteiru F\u016bkei]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Movin' On\"\n* \"Mada Ue o\"\n* \"Taboo\"\n* \"Let Me Down\"\n* \"Sora Takaku\"\n* \"Summer Splash!\"}}\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Beautiful World (Arashi album)|Beautiful World]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Rock this\"\n* \"Mada Minu Sekai e\"\n* \"Hung up on\"\n* \"Joy\"\n* \"Kono Mama Motto\"}}\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''Ura Ara Mania''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Sketch\"\n* \"Green\"}}\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Popcorn (Arashi album)|Popcorn]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Welcome to our party\"\n* \"Tabi wa Tsuzuku yo\"\n* \"Fly on Friday\"\n* \"Cosmos\"\n* \"Up to you\"}}\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Love (Arashi album)|Love]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Ai o Uta\u014d\"\n* \"P\uff65A\uff65R\uff65A\uff65D\uff65O\uff65X\"\n* \"sugar and salt\"\n* \"Starlight kiss\"}}\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[The Digitalian]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Tell me why\"\n* \"Asterisk\"\n* \"Hey Yeah!\"\n* \"Take Off !!!!!\"}}\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Japonism (Arashi album)|Japonism]]''\n|style=\"font-size: 85%;\"| {{hide||\n* \"Kokoro no Sora\"\n* \"Kimi e no Omoi\"\n* \"Rolling days\"\n* \"I