]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 2009\n| ''Uta no Onii-san''\n| Himself\n| Episode 6 guest appearance\n|-\n| ''The Quiz Show 2''\n| Satoru Kamiyama\n| Lead role\n|-\n| ''My Girl''\n| Sato\n| Episode 10 guest appearance\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 2010\n| ''[[Saigo no Yakusoku]]''\n| Yukio Tomizawa\n| Lead role with Arashi members, TV special\n|-\n| ''[[Kobe Shimbun]] no Nanokakan''\n| Tomohiko Mitsuyama\n| Lead role, [[docudrama]] special\n|-\n| ''Tokujo Kabachi!!''\n| Katsuhiro Tamura\n| Lead role\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Nazotoki wa Dinner no Ato de]]''\n|rowspan=\"3\"| Kageyama\n| Lead role\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"| 2012\n| ''Mou Yuukai Nante Shinai''\n| Cameo appearance\n|-\n| ''[[Nazotoki wa Dinner no Ato de]]''\n| Lead role, TV special\n|-\n| ''Blackboard, Teachers Who Fought Against Era''\n| Shirahama\n| Lead role (first night), 3-nights TV special\n|-\n| ''Papadol!''\n| Himself\n| Episode 1 guest appearance\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 2013\n| ''[[The Family Game (2013)|Kazoku Game]]''\n| Kouya Yoshimoto\n| Lead role\n|-\n| ''[[Nazotoki wa Dinner no Ato de|Nazotoki wa Dinner no Ato de: Senj\u014d Tantei Kageyama]]''\n|rowspan=\"2\"| Kageyama\n| Lead role, TV special\n|-\n| ''[[Nazotoki wa Dinner no Ato de|Nazotoki wa Dinner no Ato de: Kazamatsuri Keibu no Jikenbo]]''\n| Special appearance, TV special\n|-\n|2015\n|''Taishi Kakka no Ryourinin''\n| Ko Osawa\n| Lead role, TV special\n|-\n|2016\n|''Sekai Ichi Muzukashii Koi''\n|Himself\n|Episode 10 guest appearance\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n|''Kimi ni Sasageru Emblem''\n|Kazuya Takajo\n|Lead role, TV special\n|-\n|''Saki ni Umareta Dake no Boku''\n|Ryosuke Narumi\n|Lead role\n|-\n|2019\n|''[[:ja:\u30ce\u30fc\u30b5\u30a4\u30c9\u30fb\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0#\u30b2\u30b9\u30c8|No side game]]\n|Akagi Kazuki\n|Episode 10 guest appearance<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://natalie.mu/eiga/news/347416|title=\u6afb\u4e95\u7fd4\u304c\u300c\u30ce\u30fc\u30b5\u30a4\u30c9\u30fb\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u300d\u6700\u7d42\u56de\u306b\u767b\u5834\u3001\u30e9\u30b0\u30d3\u30fc\u7df4